with this beautiful woman.

110
00:06:26,548 --> 00:06:28,047
Be reasonable.

111
00:06:28,049 --> 00:06:30,616
Now, look, we're gonna push our
flights back a couple of days,

112
00:06:30,618 --> 00:06:33,318
