be Italian or something.

126
00:07:48,729 --> 00:07:51,463
Hey, buddy!
What's going on?

127
00:07:51,465 --> 00:07:54,467
- How are you, Mr. Kitner?
- Fine, fine, fine.

128
00:07:54,469 --> 00:07:57,837
